EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Shane.Richie.and.Jessie.Wallace


Celebrate 30 years of EastEnders in the company of those who know it best - the stars! Relive iconic moments and find out the real gossip from the set.

Shane and Jessie welcome you into their Walford home to celebrate 30 years of EastEnders. Relive infamous Moon moments, from halted weddings to huge family revelations
